{"tid":2201371,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] MacBook Pro iCloud 取消同步 一半相同片唔見晒","createTime":"2020-09-13T18:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T18:03:50.000Z","uid":344458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"993cafbcc1cd3426508662000750f3df5e21e70f","tid":2201371,"uid":344458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T18:03:50.000Z","msg":"本身個file係[.tmp]嚟，無up到上icloud<br />\n當時有啲相同片開到播到，有啲就唔得<br />\nCut走file name 個［.tmp]之後up上icloud，都仍然係有啲檔案開到有啲檔案開唔到<br />\n當我加返［.tmp]落file name之後，無喺icloud同步，突然喺電腦顯示，有一半相同片唔見咗，係之前開唔到嘅嗰啲黎，垃圾桶搵唔到，icloud都搵唔到<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以救下我 點樣可以救返啲相同片返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}